      "id": "9adffdf1_421032a8",
      "file_path": "vid-app-common/src/main/java/org/onap/vid/changeManagement/ChangeManagementRequest.java",
      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 97,
      "message": "1. Suggestion: I'd recommend using Objects.equals and Objects hashCode() for implementing the contract (available since jdk7). The main benefit is no reliance on 3rd party apache libs and I find them more readable. This can be easily generated using IDE tools. 2. Since you have implemented the equals/hashCode contract, it is necessary to fully test it and ensure that all conditions of equality are met. For this I'd recommend using EqualsTester provided by guava",
