      "message": "It is good practice to have the `HttpServletRequest` as a parameter. This lets an aspect to peek into the \"raw\" data, session, and such.\nFor instance, see how `EELFLoggerAdvice` is looking for `instanceof HttpServletRequest`. (Well actually, I see now that `EELFLoggerAdvice` is only checking for the first argument; so maybe need to bring param back, and reorder.)",
